                  <summary>Antiphonary for the Fast of Lent, ጾመ፡ ድጓ፡, with musical notation</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="97v" facs="003"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT2361somade"/><incipit xml:lang="gez">በ፪ በማኅትወ፡ ድራረ፡ ጾም፡ ባኡ፡ ዘወረደ፡ እምላዕሉ፡ አይሁድ፡ ሰቀሉ፡ ወሚመ፡ ኢያእመሩ፡ እግዚአ፡ ኵሉ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
